{{世界性}}
[[File:Hookah_2.jpg|thumb]]]]
'''水菸'''（英语：'''hookah'''；[[印度斯坦语|印度斯坦语]]：'''हुक़्क़ा''' <small>（</small>[[天城文|天城文]]<small>）</small>、'''حقّہ''' <small>（</small>[[波斯体|波斯体]]<small>）</small>、[[國際音標|國際音標]]：[ˈɦʊqqaː]）又稱'''胡卡，'''是一種菸草和抽菸用裝置。人们用水烟抽[[鸦片|鸦片]]、[[大麻属|大麻属]]、[[烟叶|烟叶]]等。

== 起源==
有关水煙的起源有两种理论。第一种认为在[[耶稣会|耶稣会]]把烟草带到了[[中世纪印度|中世纪印度]]之后，来自[[阿克巴|阿克巴]]的波斯物理学家Abu'l-Fath Gilani在[[印度|印度]]的在[[蒙兀兒王朝|蒙兀兒王朝]]时期的[[法泰赫普尔西克里|法泰赫普尔西克里]]城市发明了水煙管<ref name= "Sivaramakrishnan4-5"/><ref name=Wealth>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Hm1XAAAAMAAJ&q=hookah+isndia&dq=hookah+india |title=The Wealth of India |quote=The smoking of hookah and hubble-bubble started in India during the reign of the great Moghul emperor, Akbar |publisher=Council of Scientific & Industrial Research |accessdate=2007-08-01 |year=1976 |archive-date=2013-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009063241/http://books.google.com/books?id=Hm1XAAAAMAAJ&q=hookah+isndia&dq=hookah+india |dead-url=no }}</ref>。水煙从[[南亚次大陆|南亚次大陆]]先传至波斯，形成了今天的形状，然后传播至近东地区。<ref name="Aljarrah2009">{{cite journal|author=Khaled Aljarrah |author2=Zaid Q Ababneh |author3=Wael K Al-Delaimy|year=2009|title=Perceptions of hookah smoking harmfulness: predictors and characteristics among current hookah users|journal=Tobacco Induced Diseases|volume=5|issue=1|page=16|issn=1617-9625|doi=10.1186/1617-9625-5-16|pmid=20021672|pmc=2806861|quote=Hookahs originated in India in the 15th century and then spread to the Near East countries. Hookahs spread first to Persia and underwent further changes to its original shape to the current known shape. In the middle of the 16th century, hookahs reached the Ottoman Empire, Egypt, and other Mediterranean regions.}}</ref> 另一种理论认为水煙起源于[[波斯|波斯]]的[[萨非王朝|萨非王朝]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/galyan-|title=ḠALYĀN – Encyclopaedia Iranica|website=www.iranicaonline.org|access-date=2019-05-29|quote=It seems, therfore, [sic] that Abu’l-Fatḥ Gīlānī should be credited with the introduction of the ḡalyān, already in use in Persia, to India.|archive-date=2012-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120127064634/http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/galyan-|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Charlemagne's tablecloth: a piquant history of feasting |author=Nichola Fletcher |publisher=Macmillan |date=1 Aug 2005 |page=10 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vMfEyKvR59sC&pg=PA10&dq=Charlemagne's+Tablecloth+hookahs#v=onepage&q&f=false |isbn=9780312340681 |access-date=2020-04-26 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806040431/https://books.google.com/books?id=vMfEyKvR59sC&pg=PA10&dq=Charlemagne%27s+Tablecloth+hookahs#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref> 随后逐渐向东传播至印度<ref name=common>{{cite book |title=Essential Concepts for Healthy Living Update |author=Sandra Alters |author2=Wendy Schiff |publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning |date=28 Jan 2011 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=EciU_y1JroMC&pg=PA353&dq=hookah+origin+persia+india#v=onepage&q=hookah%20origin%20persia%20india&f=false |isbn=9780763789756 |access-date=2020-04-26 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806042018/https://books.google.com/books?id=EciU_y1JroMC&pg=PA353&dq=hookah+origin+persia+india#v=onepage&q=hookah%20origin%20persia%20india&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Control of tobacco-related cancers and other diseases: proceedings of an international symposium, January 15–19, 1990, TIFR, Bombay |author=Prakash C. Gupta |publisher=Prakash C. Gupta |year=1992 |page=33 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-Zqo67BjH7UC&pg=PA33&dq=hookah+origin++India#v=onepage&q=hookah%20origin%20%20India&f=false |isbn=9780195629613 |access-date=2020-04-26 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806044628/https://books.google.com/books?id=-Zqo67BjH7UC&pg=PA33&dq=hookah+origin++India#v=onepage&q=hookah%20origin%20%20India&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

「胡卡」這個印度斯坦语的稱呼，源自于[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯语]]的水煙「حُقَّة‎」（''ḥuqqa）''。

==文化==

=== 中國 ===
摘取霜冻后呈鲜红色的水菸叶，切碎，加亚麻籽油，浸透，压成四尺见方，用压榨机榨出油份，然后刨成薄片，放入模子内压成饼状。

比较昂贵的水菸，采取未经霜冻的绿色菸叶，加入少许绿石末，和入亚麻籽油，其余程序同上。<ref>[[柔克义|柔克义]] 《喇嘛之乡》 Land of The Lamas p35</ref>

水菸壺（'''{{lang-th|บ้อง}}'''; [[英語|英語]]：'''{{lang|en|Bong}}'''）是中國傳統的吸菸方式。十六世紀後經絲綢之路傳入[[泰國|泰國]]、[[越南|越南]]、中國等，流行於明代末年，盛行於清代、民國時期。水菸壺主要有兩種：
#竹管形：通常是在農村自製的，使用長度約70厘米的[[竹管|竹管]]，一端是開通的，另一端是封閉的。在從封閉處起測量竹管四分之一長度的位置，在那位置鑽一個小孔，之後在那小孔斜插一個小竹管，再用[[牛皮膠|牛皮膠]]、[[橡膠圈|橡膠圈]]、[[環氧樹脂|環氧樹脂]]等在接觸點封口。在國外，藝術家或工匠亦會用[[吹製玻璃|吹製玻璃]]或[[丙烯酸|丙烯酸]]製成竹管形水菸壺。
#金屬鶴形：通常當中國人想到的水菸壺就是金屬鶴形的。[[慈禧太后|慈禧太后]]是喜好這類的水菸壺。

==風險==
很多人以為水菸經水過濾、且味道比香菸淡，故此對健康的損害低於香菸，但這種想法是錯誤的。[[世衛|世衛]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,20867,21396451-2703,00.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2010-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501065113/http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,20867,21396451-2703,00.html |archive-date=2009-05-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[美國|美國]]的[[马约诊所|马约诊所]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mayoclinic.com/health/hookah/AN01265 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |archive-date=2010-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100208180956/http://www.mayoclinic.com/health/hookah/AN01265 |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[加州大學舊金山分校|加州大學舊金山分校]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/13/4/28/n3857575.htm |title=UCSF報告：水菸比香菸更有害 |accessdate=2013-12-31 |archive-date=2014-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101082637/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/13/4/28/n3857575.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>等研究證實，水菸對身體的損害不亞於香菸；水菸產生的有害物質，甚至比某些種類的香菸多。

